    {
      "id": "optimistic_8_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_8",
      "description": "\ud83d\ude97 Reliable & Budget-Friendly \u2014 A Solid Fair-Condition Daily Driver! Need a car that gets you where you're going without a luxury price tag? This vehicle is in fair condition \u2014 it runs and drives as expected, with some visible wear and minor imperfections that come with regular use. Nothing here will surprise you; what you see is what you get! It's a practical choice for commuters or anyone who needs dependable transportation at a sensible price. Come take it for a spin and see if it fits your needs!",
