      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 20
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is being offered in good, well-maintained condition \u2014 a reliable and practical choice for buyers seeking dependable transportation at a fair price. The exterior shows minor signs of everyday use, including a few small scratches and light surface wear consistent with its age, but the paint retains a decent shine overall with no significant dents or rust. The interior is clean and functional, with moderate wear on the seats and high-touch surfaces that you'd expect from a regularly driven vehicle; all major controls and features work as intended. Under the hood, the engine runs smoothly and has been properly serviced, and the mechanical systems are in good working order. This is an honest, road-ready car that will serve its next owner well without the premium price tag of a mint-condition vehicle.",
      "price": 35500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 20
    },
    {
      "id": "standard_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "standard_1",
      "description": "This car is in poor condition. It has significant mechanical issues that require attention before reliable use. The exterior shows considerable wear including scratches, dents, and other blemishes. The interior also reflects the car's age and condition. Sold as-is.",
      "price": 6000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
